      "width": 520,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Post-Dictionary Authoring UI\n\nThe substrate has outrun the authoring surface.\n\nBridges, class artifacts, and graph-native meaning are now real, but the UI still centers old add-node and dictionary-first flows. This graph is for bringing the authoring surface into alignment.",
