    {
      "id": "post-dictionary-authoring-ui-browser-split-note",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Browser / Editor Split",
      "position": {
        "x": 1860,
        "y": -140
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Browser / Editor Split\n\nCurrent direction:\n\n- strip the toolbar and all properties panels from the browser path\n- leave legend-driven creation and the elements browser available there\n- keep primitive creation plus all property editing in the editor path\n\nThe properties-panel family is now a premium/editor feature.\n\nDo not remove anything until interface coverage is verified.",
