      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Current Progress\n\nLanded enough to count:\n\n- browser/editor premium split is real\n- toolbar create path is gone; courtesy creation comes through legend markdown\n- visible bridge clusters now drive creation vocabulary\n- legend and selectors align around that visible source\n- generic edge creation now draws from legend-visible edge classes\n- edge properties read visible edge classes\n- selection UI now exposes class meaning, provenance, defaults, and override hints\n- bridge-mode ports display as `bridge`\n- legacy dictionary surfaces are now explicit and degraded, not default authoring paths\n\nStill active:\n\n- transition cleanup and legacy residue review",
